This paper deals with the configuration of wireless networks using drones and user mobility, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). It also involves optimization techniques for maximizing network capacity and profitability, which could be categorized under information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of incentives to influence user mobility could also be related to machine learning (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
